parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to stall or fail, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing an accident.
symptoms: The engine stalls or fails
the check engine light comes on
the vehicle may jerk or vibrate
and there may be a loud rattling or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deactivation of the driver's airbag, horn, and steering wheel controls, which can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Clicking or grinding noise from the steering wheel
airbag error light on the dashboard
horn not working
steering wheel controls not working
loss of power to the driver's side airbag.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbags to fail to deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loss of brake function can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage or failure.

car won't start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering failure light illuminates on the dashboard

the vehicle loses power steering
the steering wheel shakes or oscillates rapidly
the horn beeps incessantly
and the airbag warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating an airbag fault, and can also lead to the loss of power steering, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the horn beeps incessantly
the steering wheel buttons stop working
the clock spring breaks when turning the steering wheel
and the power steering failure light illuminates on the dashboard.
